songs.title: Sway Freestyle
songs.lyrics:
NIGGAS RATHER SEE YOU SHOT UP FORE THEY SEE YOU POP UP
CHAIN AROUND YO NECK, ALL FRESH LOOKIN PULLIN THAT DROP UP
COUPLE SUMMERS BACK NIGGAS HAD IT, I COULDN’T COP UP
BUT I WASN’T HATIN' I WAS PATIENT TO GET THIS GUAP UP
JUST LOOK AT THEY FACES, NOW I MADE IT, AND PEOPLE GOT UP..??
